Package project4

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EFTData
    Creates a summary of EFT data for a specific provider.
    ManageRecords
    Controller class containing all member and provider records.
    ManagerTerminal
    The Manager Terminal class.
    MemberRecord
    Holds and edits all information pertaining to member records.
    MemberReport
    Member Report class: this class was called by manager terminal to generate member report.
    OperatorTerminal
    Boundary class with which the Operator interacts to add, edit, and delete records.
    Program
    Main class of Project4.
    ProviderForm
    Form completed by the Provider to verify service record.
    ProviderRecord
    Holds and edits all information pertaining to provider records.
    ProviderReport
    Creates a summary report for a provider given a specific provider number.
    ProviderTerminal
    Boundary class with which the Provider interacts to add service records and provider forms.
    Record
    This is a superclass to give the ability to change and retrieve various variables for member and provider records
    ServiceRecord
    Service Records class: use for provider terminal to record services that provide to the member and and easily let manager to generate report.
